{"tid":752311,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求自稱泛民支持者未來撚阿廢同立法會議員區諾軒嘅關係","createTime":"2018-07-22T16:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T13:48:46.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"491cb3619d7209ec418d5af90e986b69c9d6b67c","tid":752311,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"昨夜會員阿廢情緖失控（佢就表示係佢仇人關愛座hunter搞佢惹起佢把火）不斷在時事台開私怨po ，咁我就去站務台講俾admin知<br />\n今日阿廢就屈我係關愛座hunter打手<br />\n咁我自然聯想係因為我去站務台舉報佢<br />\n但阿廢又話我將兩者牽上因果關係係屈佢<br />\n見佢咁愤怒，於是我又反省今日自己仲做過咩<br />\n原來係回帶咗幾個區諾軒的醜聞<br />\n而同阿廢討論時又發現佢唔聽人講嘢、中意人身攻擊十分似區諾軒同亨利在fb開火嘅態度<br />\n所以有此一問"},{"pid":"f65c453cff1d9f8104728acd9c9fd7a0c0e552d5","tid":752311,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/004417_b11bd4cff24c7a982dbbe47ad9906b02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F004417_b11bd4cff24c7a982dbbe47ad9906b02.png&h=d184fb59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/004418_ca67580fa2cc14eea0ef1161a80935ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F004418_ca67580fa2cc14eea0ef1161a80935ae.png&h=e836b2d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/004418_f9425004075fb6417e4a3c32d02ec782.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F004418_f9425004075fb6417e4a3c32d02ec782.png&h=d200b7d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4384a40b8a7dc27a5bfb70695ce0d2c9c4b8dd4a","tid":752311,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/004445_97dc6ebe9ac8ea8a1e5be6d84f34ed19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2